  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Join Our Team and Grow Your Career!</strong><br />We are a dynamic and growing company in Singapore seeking a results-driven Sales Executive to join our team. A Sales Executive is responsible for driving business growth by identifying new sales opportunities, maintaining client relationships, and achieving sales targets.<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /><strong>Prospecting and Lead Generation</strong>: Identify and pursue new sales prospects through various channels, including networking, cold calling, and online research.<br /><strong>Client Relationship Management</strong>: Build and maintain strong relationships with existing clients to ensure customer satisfaction and repeat business.<br /><strong>Sales Presentations and Negotiations</strong>: Conduct product demonstrations and negotiate contracts to close sales effectively.<br /><strong>Sales Reporting</strong>: Prepare and present sales reports to management, detailing performance against targets and market trends.<br /><strong>Collaboration</strong>: Work closely with the marketing team to align sales strategies with promotional campaigns and customer needs.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />- 2-3 years of sales experience<br />- Excellent communication and negotiation skills<br />- Self-motivated, target-driven, and results-oriented<br />- Comfortable working with numbers and meeting targets<br />- Relevant industry experience is a plus<br /><br /><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br />- Competitive base salary and commission structure<br />- Opportunities for growth and development<br />- Dynamic and supportive work environment<br />- Collaborative team culture<br />- Training and support to grow your sales skills<br /><br /><strong>Job Details:</strong><br />- Location: Singapore<br />- Salary: $3,000/month + commission<br />- Job Type: Full-time<br />- Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 9am to 6pm</p>",
